node.text: Hey Lab Fam. We are the owner/operators of Protein Lab in Buena Park. Protein Lab at the Source is a Black and Filipino owned small business. We have no ownership in the Brea location but trust we have their full support in the fight to end racism and police brutality. We take pride in employing and serving people of every race, color and background. Many of who are even police who faithfully support our shop and serve our community. It was always our desire for Protein Lab in Buena Park to be a place that promotes unity over division. We wanted to take our time to issue a public statement in an effort to not be irresponsible with our words in one of the most important moments in our lifetime. Please make no mistake that we are fully supportive of the #Blacklivesmatter movement and are praying that it brings about real change throughout our whole country. We are also praying for the safety of all the protestors and police officers everywhere. Currently we are doing our research to determine our best route to take action on and off of social media for both the short and long term. We encourage all to do the same. Thank you for all your love and support since the first day we opened our doors. We are proud and love to be in the community of Buena Park.
